{"tid":2346282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"料中歐領導人本港時間晚上八時宣布達成中歐投資協定","createTime":"2020-12-30T06:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T12:45:04.000Z","uid":278587,"like":9,"dislike":79,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"24215764a1a6157001e2c46e50751b3c447c8502","tid":2346282,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:59:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=418442\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418442&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=37d5835b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418442&h=ac5b92e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=418442</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】中國和歐盟領導人據報將於本港時間晚上八時舉行視像會議，宣布達成中歐投資協定，擴大歐洲企業對中國多個領域的市場准入。<br />\n<br />\n歷時七年的中歐投資協定談判或有突破。彭博報道，歐洲理事會主席米歇爾、歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩、輪任國主席、德國總理默克爾周三會與國家主席習近平舉行視像會議，宣布完成談判，就協定達成政治層面共識，最終文本將在數個月內敲定。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟官員透露，協定主要目標是改正中歐不對等的市場准入待遇，中方主要承諾擴大歐洲企業在中國的市場准入，覆蓋飛機製造、雲端服務、金融和醫療等多個行業，協定又明文禁止強制技術轉移。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟則承諾維持對中國投資的既有開放程度，稍為加大開放能源批發和零售以及可再生能源市場。<br />\n<br />\n對於歐盟關注中國被指強迫新疆維吾爾人勞動的問題，據有關的歐盟官員指，中方承諾為簽署國際勞工組織有關強迫勞動的基本公約，作出持續努力，然而協定必須通過歐洲議會。有議員表明，基於中國的人權狀況會反對協定。<br />\n<br />\n就在視像會議舉行前一日，歐盟連番就中國人權問題發聲，包括要求中方立即釋放涉嫌偷越邊境的12名港人，並安排他們盡快回港。聲明又批評審訊非公開進行，外交代表和家屬不能聽審，被告的公平審訊權未獲尊重。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟亦關注曾到武漢報道新冠疫情的內地公民記者張展被判囚，說根據可靠消息，張展被拘留時曾遭嚴刑和虐待，健康狀況嚴重惡化，要求中國立即釋放她。"},{"pid":"25852f18f1b0f17d51aba5d515363f8bf0b69727","tid":2346282,"uid":155095,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:00:40.000Z","msg":"習近平落完歐盟面<br />\n<br />\n歐盟都要繼續奶共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2750000/2753239/0915003_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2750000%2F2753239%2F0915003_1024.png&h=9ff03cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/15151701/template2-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.hkgolden.media%2Fcompress%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F15151701%2Ftemplate2-1.png&h=33cf8420&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0023674a49b81cd16820a04c7f8a9364e385bb87","tid":2346282,"uid":144626,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:02:25.000Z","msg":"布歐投資協定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531a4f04ed2c6dadf1a58bb4c9c5c2e2d46f9c79","tid":2346282,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中歐又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1780440d676bc0accd8d935df9b815706e39befc","tid":2346282,"uid":26770,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:37:42.000Z","msg":"協定又明文禁止強制技術轉移<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389a6f043a48e07ff7315b57b4ff7a7554ec1705","tid":2346282,"uid":40267,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"自己用保護主義扶起國企強佔市場份額<br />\n依加先比你入到毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=就算今日支那開google入去一樣唔掂<br />\n班人用baidu用左十幾年點會用你google呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41907f6b289b8390d7326250c785a9aa6384196","tid":2346282,"uid":156913,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1780440d676bc0accd8d935df9b815706e39befc","tid":2